Business Problem: Standardizing Customer Names
Problem: Customer names were entered manually and have inconsistent spacing and capitalization (" john smith ", "MARY SUE"). This makes communication look unprofessional.
Task: Clean the column of names: remove all extra leading/trailing whitespace and standardize all entries to "Title Case" (e.g., "John Smith").

df['first_name']=df['first_name'].str.strip().str.title()
df['last_name']=df['last_name'].str.strip().str.title()

df['first_name']=df['first_name'].str.replace(r'\s+', ' ', regex=True)
df['last_name']=df['last_name'].str.replace(r'\s+', ' ', regex=True)
